{"text_id":71239,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," investigate"," the"," properties"," and"," characteristics"," of"," nearly"," horizon","-","sk","imming"," orbits"," in"," Kerr"," space","times",","," both"," circular"," and"," non","-","circular","."," These"," orbits",","," which"," come"," very"," close"," to"," the"," event"," horizon"," of"," a"," Kerr"," black"," hole"," without"," crossing"," it",","," exhibit"," intriguing"," behavior"," and"," have"," potential"," implications"," for"," various"," astro","physical"," phenomena",".","\n\n","Our"," study"," employs"," a"," combination"," of"," analytical"," and"," numerical"," methods",","," utilizing"," the"," mathematical"," framework"," of"," general"," relativity"," and"," the"," Kerr"," metric","."," We"," derive"," conditions"," for"," the"," existence"," and"," stability"," of"," these"," orbits",","," taking"," into"," account"," the"," spin"," of"," the"," black"," hole"," and"," the"," properties"," of"," the"," test"," particles","."," We"," also"," explore"," the"," effects"," of"," the"," black"," hole","'","s"," gravitational"," pull"," and"," frame","-","dragging"," on"," the"," orbital"," motion",".","\n\n","The"," key"," results"," of"," our"," work"," include"," the"," identification"," of"," novel"," features"," in"," the"," structure"," of"," circular"," and"," non","-","circular"," nearly"," horizon","-","sk","imming"," orbits",","," and"," the"," quantification"," of"," their"," dependence"," on"," the"," black"," hole","'","s"," spin"," and"," the"," test"," particle","'","s"," properties","."," In"," particular",","," we"," find"," that"," non","-","circular"," orbits"," can"," exhibit"," a"," rich"," variety"," of"," behaviors",","," including"," oscillatory"," motion"," and"," chaotic"," trajectories","."," Additionally",","," we"," demonstrate"," that"," circular"," orbits"," can"," be"," destabili","zed"," by"," the"," black"," hole","'","s"," spin",","," leading"," to"," a"," rapid"," plunge"," into"," the"," event"," horizon",".","\n\n","These"," findings"," contribute"," to"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," strong","-","field"," regime"," of"," Kerr"," space","times"," and"," have"," implications"," for"," the"," study"," of"," accretion"," disks",","," gravitational"," wave"," signals"," from"," extreme"," mass"," ratio"," inspir","als",","," and"," the"," searches"," for"," signatures"," of"," spinning"," black"," holes"," in"," astro","physical"," observations","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}